Its an eclipse project, im using Girdle currently
We have to rewrite it using Nomad Java SDK (https://github.com/hashicorp/nomad-java-sdk)
Job Modifier is a java http server, it will take requests to launch jobs, modify running jobs and undeploy running jobs.
Nomad tuts to understand this project : https://www.nomadproject.io/intro/getting-started/install.html